{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-5", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "マスカレードへの招待状", "storyInfo": "夢の中でも以前の記憶を保っていた睦は、このままレム・ビリトンに住む平凡な少女として夢の中で生きようと決めていた。睦を連れ出そうとする祥子だったが、夢の中で以前より幸せそうに暮らしている様子の睦を見て葛藤し、睦が演奏をする中でその場を逃げ出した。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我ら共に笑い、共に泣こう。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>華やかな舞台で、賑やかな一人芝居を演じよう。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我、死を恐れるなかれ。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g9_warmrabbitnest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥、飲んで。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありがとうございます。喉の痛みが少し治まりましたわ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よかった。ほら、これ。レム・ビリトンは砂地だから、水とゴーグルがないと、生きられない。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pcket", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は睦から渡されたものを両手でぎゅっと握りしめた。水の入った袋が圧力で膨らみ、今にも破裂しそうだ。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥、ちょっと変。気分悪い？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いえ、何でもありませんわ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、わたくしのこと……覚えているんですの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これまで、わたくしたちでしてきたことも？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん、全部、覚えてる。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その言葉を聞いて、祥子はようやく少しの落ち着きを取り戻し、辺りの景色を見渡した――"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二人はこれまで狭い坑道を奥へ奥へと進み、この場所までたどり着いた。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗い、じめじめとした場所。ランタンと暖炉の火だけが微かに周囲を照らしている。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ベッドと食卓の間には一人が通れるほどのスペースしかない。しかし食卓に置かれたコップの数から、睦以外もここに住んでいることが伺える。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦……ここでどのくらい暮らしているんですの？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一年くらい……ううん、もっと長いかも。どれくらい経ったか、感じなくなった。ここなら難しいことは考えなくていいから。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは違います……時間の感覚がないのは、ここが夢の中だからですわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、どうしてこのような夢を……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢……？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、あなたに大事なことをお伝えします。ここは現実ではありません、今すぐに――", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あら――睦ちゃん、もう帰ってきてたの〜？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_kneelsnow_s", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背後から走ってきた女性が、そのままの勢いで睦に抱きついた。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "マ、ママ……埃、ついてるから、こすったらだめ……", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もう！　丸一日も会ってなかったんだから、ちょっとくらい抱きついたっていいじゃない！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お客さん、来てるから……", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あら、さきちゃん！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うちに来るの、ずいぶん久しぶりね？", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "みなみさん……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もう〜、そんなよそよそしい呼び方じゃなくて、「みなみちゃん」って呼んで？", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん、私も、たまにそう呼ぶ。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦、いつからみなみさんとこれほど仲良くなりましたの……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あら、私と睦ちゃんはずっと仲がいいのよ？　だって親子なんだから。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ところで睦ちゃん、今日の成果はどうだった？", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きゅうりジュース、いつもよりちょっと多めに売れた……多分、暑かったから。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦がポケットに入っていた巾着をそっと開けると、中には硬貨が数枚入っていた。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん――睦ちゃん、偉い！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ねえ、私のほうも見て。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#15$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ママ、すごい……", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#15$3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふ、今日は服のお直しを頼む人が何故かいつもより多かったの！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "パパも、工事現場で一日中ずっと働いてたよ。お昼を持って行った時、埃まみれのパパを見たらちょっと可哀想になっちゃってね。仕事が終わったらちょっとだけ飲んでいいよって言っちゃった。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今頃、仕事の人と一杯飲んでるかも。一応「早く帰ってきてね」とも言ったけどね。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちょうどさきちゃんも来たことだし、せっかくだから、みんなでご馳走にしよっか！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "みんなで揃って食べられるの、嬉しい。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうよ、今日はいつもより余裕があるし、たくさん食べなきゃ。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さきちゃんも、遠慮しなくていいからね！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥、どうしたの？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "い、いえ……なんでも……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目の前にある、裕福さとはかけ離れた家。剥き出しの土壁、弱々しく光るオイルランプ……"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうして睦の夢は、こんな所に……"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦ちゃん、みなみちゃん……あら？　こちらの方は？", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥……私の幼馴染。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初めまして。", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#4$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夕食でもご一緒にと思って来たんですが、いかがですか？", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "たくさん作ってきたので、ぜひ食べてください！", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……申し訳ないわ、そんなの。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ご近所さんから聞いたんです。睦ちゃん家の煙突から、もう何日も煙が出てないって……", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#10$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（お腹をさする）……", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに、前回のパーティーからもう一ヶ月くらい経ちますし。", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "皆さん言ってましたよ。また睦ちゃんの演奏を聴きたいって。", "name": "ウォーミー"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そういうことなら……睦ちゃん、どう？", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "え……私の演奏？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さきちゃんも聴きたいでしょ？　睦ちゃんの演奏、何回聴いても素晴らしいの！", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうだ！　いっそうちでパーティーをしましょう！　実はさっきまで、みんなも食事に誘いたいなって思ってたのよ。", "name": "睦の母"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥は、どう思う？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうね……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしは……睦がどうしたいかが大事だと思いますわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……うん、私、弾きたい。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"